WEBVTT

00:03:57.797 --> 00:04:00.257
and they're just trying
to figure out what happened.

00:04:00.281 --> 00:04:02.612
(Laughter) (Applause)

00:04:02.636 --> 00:04:05.071
But you're over here listening.

00:04:05.706 --> 00:04:08.433
And you're listening
to their made-up scenario

00:04:08.457 --> 00:04:09.830
that now can impact

00:04:09.854 --> 00:04:13.102
how you choose to interact
with that person throughout the day.

00:04:13.907 --> 00:04:17.598
Whether we're creating
fake stories in our head

00:04:17.622 --> 00:04:20.323
or listening to other people's
made-up stories,

00:04:20.347 --> 00:04:22.026
it needs to stop.

00:04:22.819 --> 00:04:24.599
The goal in this step:

00:04:24.623 --> 00:04:27.699
stop stressing over things
that haven't happened.

